{"tid":2335193,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"yama / BIN 上咗 The First Take","createTime":"2020-12-21T16:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T17:02:04.000Z","uid":387649,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9b0b88e8be563742450738b7ef0535ef0910f713","tid":2335193,"uid":387649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T16:14:06.000Z","msg":"見連登冇人講，咁就我講<br />\n<br />\n本身係 Vocaloid 翻唱歌手嘅 yama 早兩日上咗 The First Take<br />\n咁我諗有聽開嘅都知道<br />\n上年年尾開始喺Youtube 營運嘅 The First Take 已經搵咗好多出名嘅歌手，<br />\n用 Acoustic 嘅方式 1 take 過演奏自己嘅作品<br />\n咁如果唱功冇返多少力水，其實就好難咁做到<br />\n當中依家無人不曉嘅LiSA 都已經唱咗好多作品<br />\n另外幾位同Vocaloid 有關嘅例如 YOASOBI，Chico with Honeyworks 亦到有演出過<br />\nChico 同 YOASOBI 印象應該除左LIVE 活動我唔肯定之外，應該係未現過真身<br />\n咁今次黎到 yama 表演佢同V家作曲家 くじら 嘅作品 春を告げる<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q5e0C6xizVY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dq5e0C6xizVY&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=3a999644\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q5e0C6xizVY</a><br />\n<br />\n中性帶點磁性嘅音色<br />\n再家上大小提琴、鋼琴嘅配樂同原版電子風相比別有一番味道<br />\n而原版都已經去到5000萬嘅播放數<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DC6JppqHkaM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDC6JppqHkaM&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=1c725f4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DC6JppqHkaM</a><br />\n<br />\n咁就講返少少背景先<br />\nyama 應該係兩年前開始喺YT放片<br />\n初期主要翻唱Vocaloid 嘅歌<br />\n早有味道應該係呢首<br />\n唱到歌詞嗰種憤世味出黎 <br />\n[cover]bin/yama<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W92y4dfy4wg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DW92y4dfy4wg&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=0b3b73d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W92y4dfy4wg</a><br />\n<br />\n後來佢開始同呢首歌嘅作曲家Vocaloid P 猫アレルギー合作組左隊叫 BIN嘅樂隊<br />\n反應都幾唔錯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w73Ks2WX_XQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw73Ks2WX_XQ&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=2c47dd1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w73Ks2WX_XQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ufVRe3aifu0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DufVRe3aifu0&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=444f1a2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ufVRe3aifu0</a><br />\n<br />\n咁佢之後都仲有繼續唱V家嘅歌，其中我自己最鍾意嘅係<br />\nあぷえらP 作嘅チョコレートミルク<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hm2D1O_Gx9c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dhm2D1O_Gx9c&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=1b7eb82e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hm2D1O_Gx9c</a><br />\n<br />\nyama 第一次同くじら合作應該喺呢一首 ねむるまち<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ePBjUMEeqBw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DePBjUMEeqBw&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=e6f2db99\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ePBjUMEeqBw</a><br />\n本身首歌有 Vocaloid Version 想聽嘅話可以買碟...<br />\n<br />\n然後再翻唱くじらP嘅 幽霊東京<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qhTkYIQQKYk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqhTkYIQQKYk&d=YgirQyY3AADlg18%2F%2B2KZ%2FRckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=9c1d8cde\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qhTkYIQQKYk</a><br />\n<br />\n之後再家上春を告げる同佢哋合作嘅其他作品就紅到依家上The First Take<br />\n個人都好欣賞くじらP可以平衡喺V家同商業作品兩邊嘅發展<br />\n<del>唔似得n-buna 咁一去就冇回頭</del><br />\n然後佢作嘅歌，快歌節奏感強，慢歌亦都悅耳<br />\n希望佢地都可以KEEP住依家嘅步伐再創作更多嘅作品<br />\n同埋都高興自己有跟開嘅歌手/作曲家能夠成名<br />\n<br />\n------<br />\n<br />\n咁就寫住咁多先，本身諗住入成人台先開連登ACCOUNT <br />\n但又忽然想寫...<br />\n<br />\n我自己就聽Vocaloid 多，有野可以PM我，係咁多先"},{"pid":"09d801b35f5b72d77eeca787dbc82f221c0fe147","tid":2335193,"uid":386567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T17:51:19.000Z","msg":"巴打識貨呀！冇諗過會有人識！佢把聲我真係冇乜抵抗力"},{"pid":"5454de5ca23eb3f2530f265ab35d8c44525197d0","tid":2335193,"uid":387649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"09d801b35f5b72d77eeca787dbc82f221c0fe147","tid":2335193,"uid":386567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T17:51:19.000Z","msg":"巴打識貨呀！冇諗過會有人識！佢把聲我真係冇乜抵抗力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T19:58:12.000Z","msg":"其實都算幾紅..."},{"pid":"6e31a0b8e41acdfaffd35cd6a95d984e0b0387fb","tid":2335193,"uid":372796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T08:12:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d15230c43e304a7c196aed329faff6e0983d195e","tid":2335193,"uid":15302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:07:59.000Z","msg":"把聲幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底係咪女既？"},{"pid":"544b4c09e63a1b309351f8f9796c63fdea0889b6","tid":2335193,"uid":387649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d15230c43e304a7c196aed329faff6e0983d195e","tid":2335193,"uid":15302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:07:59.000Z","msg":"把聲幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底係咪女既？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:08:22.000Z","msg":"女黎啦"},{"pid":"ab6028b0b4dd2b6e9193bfccc3d5eb4fc4e35f97","tid":2335193,"uid":387649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"2.34首OP應該紅過套野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249bcb79d52d40a14d6f3cd3b34c92b8a011d3bd","tid":2335193,"uid":15302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"544b4c09e63a1b309351f8f9796c63fdea0889b6","tid":2335193,"uid":387649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d15230c43e304a7c196aed329faff6e0983d195e","tid":2335193,"uid":15302,"like":0,"dislik